FBIS4-36869 "drnes114dd_94014" FBIS-NES-94-114 Daily Report 14 Jun 1994 Palestinian Affairs National Authority Bans Strikes in Gaza, Jericho National Authority Bans Strikes in Gaza, Jericho NC1006181894 Jerusalem AL-NAHAR in Arabic 9 Jun pp 3, 7 NC1006181894 Jerusalem AL-NAHAR Arabic BFN [Report by 'Abd-al-Ra'uf al-Arna'ut in Jerusalem] [Excerpt] A responsible source in the Palestinian National Authority in the Jericho area has stated that strikes in Palestinian sovereign areas will be strictly prohibited. In an exclusive statement to AL-NAHAR, the source said: Strikes express the rejection of a certain policy. However, under a national authority which represents the people, there is no reason to hold strikes. He added: Strikes are allowed in other parts of the West Bank because they are a legitimate activity to remove the occupation. [passage omitted]
